These are recomended setting from chat where you have set margins and padding to zero globally:
(*, *::before, *::after {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin:0;/**Both eliminates default browser spacing**/
    padding:0;
    }
)

Code starts here!
/*Spacing for h,p and small tags*/
h1 {margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 16px;}
h2 {margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 14px;}
h3 {margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 12px;}
p {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.5;}
small{margin-top: 4px;margin-bottom: 4px; 
   margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0;line-height: 1.4;}


